      <title>民意调查显示，Sheinbaum 在墨西哥比赛中领先 17 分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/sheinbaum-holds-17-point-lead-in-mexico-race-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，墨西哥总统候选人克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆(Claudia Sheinbaum)在六月大选正式竞选阶段一个月后领先17个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/sheinbaum-holds-17-point-lead-in-mexico-race-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦的公路旅行有一个主题：放眼全球，吃当地美食</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yellen-s-road-trips-have-a-theme-think-global-eat-local</link>
      <description><![CDATA[我们已经知道珍妮特·耶伦的理想午餐约会对象是已故的英国传奇经济学家约翰·梅纳德·凯恩斯。根据她担任财政部长的习惯，我们可以猜测地点将是凯恩斯家乡剑桥的一家当地酒吧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yellen-s-road-trips-have-a-theme-think-global-eat-local</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在地方选举中失利削弱了无敌领袖的形象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-01/erdogan-s-shock-defeat-in-turkey-local-polls-dubai-s-allure-for-russians-dims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 在市政选举中遭受了前所未有的失败，主要反对派团体在曾经由执政党正义与发展党 (AK Party) 统治的地区取得了前所未有的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-04-01/erdogan-s-shock-defeat-in-turkey-local-polls-dubai-s-allure-for-russians-dims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 13:47:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯坦布尔胜利后，埃尔多安的宿敌成为头号竞争对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkey-election-results-istanbul-mayor-ekrem-imamoglu-takes-fight-to-erdogan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯坦布尔市长埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁巩固了自己作为总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的头号对手的地位，因为他将统治范围扩大到了该国最大的城市，这一胜利可能使他有一天能够接替土耳其任期最长的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/turkey-election-results-istanbul-mayor-ekrem-imamoglu-takes-fight-to-erdogan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 10:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
